&quot;I never should have given up animation rights.&quot;  
All pieces print without support or rafts.<br />
Most pieces are glued together.<br />
The character stands on its own with the third leg being the sword of destiny. Glue this on last to get the right stance and balance.   
&quot;You look like you're fighting dragons. From the future.&quot;  
